00:18:15.556 --> 00:18:20.676
And recreating that world, you
know, we wanted to stay true

00:18:20.676 --> 00:18:24.066
to the essence of the design
while still pushing the limits

00:18:24.066 --> 00:18:26.516
of what we can do
now that it's 2013.

