00:26:01.446 --> 00:26:03.736
So, what could possibly
go wrong, right?

00:26:04.996 --> 00:26:06.706
So it'll be exciting
for me, hopefully,

00:26:06.706 --> 00:26:08.606
exciting for you
as well to do this.

00:26:08.716 --> 00:26:10.566
So, all right.

00:26:11.486 --> 00:26:12.546
So this is the new Mac Pro

00:26:12.546 --> 00:26:14.806
and this is MARI running
on the new Mac Pro.

00:26:14.806 --> 00:26:17.566
And this is how I get the model
from the modeling department.

00:26:17.566 --> 00:26:18.256
It's gray.

00:26:18.256 --> 00:26:20.936
It doesn't have any detail
yet because it's my job

00:26:21.276 --> 00:26:22.726
to add the detail
to the character.

00:26:22.796 --> 00:26:25.266
