00:35:25.846 --> 00:35:29.026
But with every character
in a 3D film,

00:35:29.426 --> 00:35:32.076
there are multiple channels
that define different parts

00:35:32.076 --> 00:35:33.326
of what the character
looks like.

00:35:33.646 --> 00:35:35.196
