00:47:22.181 --> 00:47:24.181
[ Laughter ]

00:47:24.346 --> 00:47:24.926
So there he is.

00:47:24.926 --> 00:47:27.236
And we've got both of these
characters and I can see them

00:47:27.236 --> 00:47:29.016
