00:47:29.046 --> 00:47:33.226
I can see them right here
and that is so helpful.

00:47:33.226 --> 00:47:37.596
It's so amazing to be able to
find and identify any problems

00:47:37.596 --> 00:47:39.146
that we have by having
these characters

00:47:39.146 --> 00:47:39.886
in the same room together.

00:47:39.886 --> 00:47:42.726
And I can even bring
in the set and see them

00:47:42.726 --> 00:47:44.746
with their shadows
in this environment.

00:47:45.486 --> 00:47:47.026
And it's been so amazing.

00:47:47.066 --> 00:47:49.596
And, you know, I think
that's it for the demo.

00:47:50.096 --> 00:47:53.566
I've-- it's been such a
privilege to speak to you today

00:47:53.566 --> 00:47:55.136
