this amazing hardware.

00:47:55.136 --> 00:47:56.486
I can't wait to get
my hands on one.

00:47:56.486 --> 00:47:58.416
I can't wait 'til the fall.

00:47:59.096 --> 00:48:01.266
And I've been so-- it's been
such a privilege to work

00:48:01.266 --> 00:48:02.176
on Monsters University.

